<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FacultyHub</title>
    {{!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="faculty_profileStyle.css"> --}}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <script src='https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js' crossorigin='anonymous'></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    {{!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="public/facultyProfile.css"> --}}
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        body {
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* header part*/
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background-color: #0D1B2A;
            color: white;
            align-items: center;
            height: 8vh;
            padding-left: 7vh;
            padding-right: 5vh;
            border: 2px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);
            border-bottom-left-radius: 3.5vh;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 3.5vh;
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }

        header a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 2vh;
            margin: 1vh;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        header button {
            margin: 1vh;
        }

        nav {
            gap: 2vh;

        }

        nav>a {
            padding: 10px;


        }

        .logged {
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: solid 3px white;
            background-color: white;
            color: #000000;

        }


        /* footer part*/
        footer {
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 2vh;
            padding-top: 1vh;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #588414;
            color: white;
        }

        .left a {
            display: block;
            padding: 1vh 4vh 2vh 2vh;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: #ffffff;
            /* Link color */
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .right {
            position: static;
            text-align: left;
            width: 28vh;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .right h2 {
            position: static;
            text-align: left;
        }

        /* main part */

        form {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 3vh;
        }

        form.example input[type=text] {
            padding: 11px 25px;
            font-size: 17px;
            background: #070505;
            border: 1px solid black;
            color: white;
            width: 30vw;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 2.5vw;
            border-top-left-radius: 2.5vw;
        }

        form.example button {
            width: 5vh;
            padding: 1vh;
            background: #000000;
            color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            font-size: 17px;
            border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);
            border-left: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 2.5vw;
            border-top-right-radius: 2.5vw;
        }

        form.example button:hover {
            background: #060079;
        }

        main h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 15px;
            font-size: 3.5vh;
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }


        .wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: left;
            align-items: center;
            /*  padding-left: 123px; */

        }

        .user-card {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 1vh;
            padding: 3vh;
            width: 140vh;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding-left: 5vw;

        }

        .user-card-img {
            float: left;
            z-index: 3;
            box-shadow: 8px 8px 4px rgb(87, 105, 107);
            /* box-shadow: 2vh 0 3vh -1vh rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);  */
            border-radius: 1vw;
        }

        .user-card-img img {
            width: 30vh;
            height: 30vh;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 7px 7px 7px 7px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .user-card-info {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .user-card-info h2 {
            font-size: 3vh;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            padding-left: 0.7vw;

        }

        .user-card-info p {
            font-size: 2.5vh;
            padding-top: 1.5vh;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            padding-left: 0.7vw;

        }

        .user-card-info p span {
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
            .user-card {
                flex-direction: row;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .user-card-img {
                margin-right: 20px;
                margin-bottom: 0;
            }

            .user-card-info {
                text-align: left;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .wrapper {
                padding-top: 0.5%;

            }

            .user-card:before {
                width: 300%;
                height: 10vh;
                transform: rotate(0);
            }

            .user-card-info h2 {
                margin-top: 1vh;
                font-size: 3vh;
            }

            .user-card-info p span {
                display: block;
                margin-bottom: 1vh;
                font-size: 2.5vh;
            }
        }

        */ .container {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);

        }

        .tab_box {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: space-around;


        }

        .tab_box .tab_btn {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 2.5vh;
            font-weight: 500;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid white;
            color: #0D1B2A;
            background: none;
            border: #bab3b3 1.5px solid;
            padding: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: sans-serif;

        }

        .tab_box .tab_btn.active {
            color: white;
            background-color: #0D1B2A;
            border-radius: 1vh;


        }

        .tab_box .tab_btn:hover {
            color: white;
            background-color: #0D1B2A;
            box-shadow: 0 1vh 1vh rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            /* box-shadow: 0 8px 16px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2), 0 6px 20px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.19); */
            /* transform: translateY(2px);  */
            border-radius: 1vh;


        }

        .content_box {
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .content_box .content {
            display: none;
            animation: moving .5s ease;

        }

        @keyframes moving {
            from {
                transform: translateX(50px);
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                transform: translateX(0px);
                opacity: 1;
            }

        }

        .content_box .content.active {
            display: block;
        }

        .content_box .content h2 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5vh;
        }

        .content {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            font-size: 2vh;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .tab_box {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
            }


        }
    </style>
    <!--  <script defer src="active.js"></script> -->
</head>

<body>
    {{>header}}

    <main>
        <h1>Faculty Details of {{faculty.institute}}</h1>

        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="user-card">
                <div class="user-card-img">
                    <img alt="Faculty Image" class="img-fluid" id="img1"
                        src="data:{{faculty.image.contentType}};base64,{{faculty.image.data}}"
                        onerror="faculty.onerror=null; faculty.src='https://www.bing.com/images/search?q=blank%20profile%20image&FORM=IQFRBA&id=E9A45CA64F9637C3256BDC7FD0943D2B5517A4F3'">
                    </img>
                </div>
                <div class="user-card-info">
                    <h2>Faculty Name: {{faculty.name}} </h2>
                    <p><span>Institute: {{faculty.institute}}</span></p>
                    <p><span>Email-address: {{faculty.email}}</span> </p>
                    <p><span>Contact No* : {{faculty.contactNo}} </span></p>
                    <p><span>Address*: {{faculty.address}} </span></p>
                    <p><span>Website: <a href="{{faculty.website}}">{{faculty.website}}</a></span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="tab_box">
                <button class="tab_btn">Details</button>
                <button class="tab_btn">Publication</button>
                <button class="tab_btn">Internships</button>
                <button class="tab_btn">Projects</button>

            </div>
            <div class="content_box">
                <div class="content">
                    <h2>Details</h2>
                    <p>Education: {{faculty.education}}</p>
                    <p>Field of specialalization: {{faculty.specialization}}</p>
                    <p>Courses Taught*:{{faculty.coursesTaught}}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h2>Publication</h2>
                    {{!-- <p>Title 1</p>
                <p>Title 2</p>
                <p>Title 3</p>
                <p>Title 4</p>
                <p>Title 5</p> --}}
                    {{faculty.publications}}
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h2>Internships</h2>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. Ea consequatur quia et sequi molestias ea sapiente deleniti? Et Quis
                        ipsam est laborum cumque et iusto quod At voluptas magni. Quo commodi praesentium rem quas
                        maiores est atque earum eos asperiores omnis et ratione autem et facere deserunt.</p>

                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h2>Projects</h2>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. Ea consequatur quia et sequi molestias ea sapiente deleniti? Et Quis
                        ipsam est laborum cumque et iusto quod At voluptas magni. Quo commodi praesentium rem quas
                        maiores est atque earum eos asperiores omnis et ratione autem et facere deserunt.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <script>
            const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab_btn');
            const all_content = document.querySelectorAll('.content');


            tabs.forEach((tab, index) => {
                tab.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                    tabs.forEach(tab => { tab.classList.remove('active') });
                    tab.classList.add('active');

                    all_content.forEach(content => { content.classList.remove('active') })
                    all_content[index].classList.add('active');

                })
            })

        </script>


    </main>

    {{>footer}}
</body>

</html>